## 🧠 PART 1 — What is This Project? (The Big Picture)

This is a **real-time, Kahoot-style quiz platform** built for a classroom setting. It has three types of users:

| Role | What they can do |
|---|---|
| **Teacher** | Create quizzes (manually/AI/PDF), host live quiz rooms, monitor student progress in real-time, see leaderboards |
| **Student** | Join quizzes with a code, answer questions, see scores, view history |
| **Admin** | Manage the platform (admin dashboard) |

> [!NOTE]
> Self-registration is **disabled**. Only an admin can create accounts. This was done intentionally to prevent random students from signing up.

